# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Motuva pipeline — .gitignore
# Keep the repo to SOURCE + small config only. Large assets and secrets are
# shipped to the pod out-of-band (see SETUP.md), never committed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets / runtime env ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# a.env (and any *.env) holds real HF_TOKEN / REMOVE_BG_API_KEY + machine paths.
# The committable template is .env.example (kept via the negation below).
*.env
!.env.example

# ── Large model / index / render assets (ship out-of-band, NOT via git) ─────
# ~1.4 GB total; .pth and .blend exceed GitHub's 100 MB/file limit.
# Ignore EVERYTHING inside assets/ except the tracked placeholder README, so the
# folder still exists in the repo (see assets/PLACEHOLDER_README.md).
assets/*
!assets/PLACEHOLDER_README.md
*.pth
*.pt
*.blend
*.npy

# ── Outputs / scratch / checkpoints ─────────────────────────────────────────
testing-images-results/
exports/
# Batch input/output image dumps (car adverts w/ number plates — PII, and large).
Images/
*.zip
*.tgz
# warm-worker temp dirs (created under the OS temp dir, but ignore if local)
motuva_in/
motuva_plates/

# ── Python ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
build/
dist/
.venv/
venv/
env/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# ── Editor / OS / tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.agents/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

.agents
